Libraries

library(brms)
source("rcomp.R")
lambda_sim <- rnorm(1)
nu_sim <- rlnorm(1)

print(paste("lambda: ", exp(lambda_sim), "nu: ", nu_sim))
## [1] "lambda:  0.0832354267117676 nu:  0.756732239477989"
df <- rcomp(300, exp(lambda_sim), nu_sim)

print(paste("mean samples: ", mean(df)))
## [1] "mean samples:  0.0966666666666667"
barplot(table(df), col = "steelblue", main = "Simulated COM-Poisson")
